週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1introduction: spatial planning in general2urbnisms and strategic planning3on network urbanism4on network urbanism5on landscape urbanism6on landscape urbanism7on ecological urbanism8on typological urbanism9case study report10assignment of a team-based practice11mapping and data analysis12spatial argument formation13objectives for a strategic project14reevaluating and re-orgnizing15reevaluating and re-orgnizing16priliminary programming for the project17internal review (pin-ups)18outside rview 

